Problem Statement
Lack of integrated platforms for devotional travel planning combined with cultural storytelling.
Simple Architecture Diagram
+------------------+
|      User        |
| (Web Browser)    |
+--------+---------+
         |
         v
+------------------+
|   Frontend UI    |
| (HTML, CSS, JS)  |
+--------+---------+
         |
         v
+---------------------------+
